# Project constitution

- Read `MISSION.md` and `AGENTS.md` before planning major changes.
- Adults only (18+). Fail closed when age eligibility cannot be established.
- No exact location, precise distance, or real-time proximity alerts to peers.
- No operator access to ordinary profiles, photos, or messages.
- No sale or ad-training use of dating/sexuality/location/message/photo data.
- No paywall on block, report, age assurance, encryption, or basic discovery.
- Prefer the smallest coherent slice; create an ADR before new architecture.
- Staging deploy only after staging account identity verification.
- Never deploy production, submit to app stores, or fabricate approvals.
- Never weaken encryption, age, block/report, retention, or audit controls to unblock work.
- Evidence before confidence: do not claim tests passed without command output.
